      "content": "When people offer simple platitudes, it can feel dismissive of such deep pain, and I hear how exhausted you are from carrying this weight. Please recognize that what you are feeling is a profound grief, and it is valid to not feel \"better\" right now. If the weight is truly unbearable, reaching out to a grief counselor or a support hotline can provide a space where someone truly understands this specific ache.",
      "source": "target",
